Package: linux-headers-generic-lts-saucy
Architecture: i386 amd64 armhf
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-generic
Description: Generic Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest generic 12.10 kernel headers
 available.

Package: linux-image-generic-lts-saucy
Architecture: i386 amd64 armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-generic, linux-firmware
Description: Generic Linux kernel image
 This package will always depend on the latest generic 12.10 kernel image
 available.

Package: linux-generic-lts-saucy
Architecture: i386 amd64 armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-generic-lts-saucy, linux-headers-generic-lts-saucy
Description: Generic Linux kernel image and headers
 This package will always depend on the latest generic 12.10 kernel image
 and headers packages available.

# Update this meta package to depend on the 14.04 LTS kernel when Saucy goes EOL.

Package: linux-generic-lts-saucy-eol-upgrade
Architecture: i386 amd64 armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-generic-lts-saucy
Description: Complete Generic Linux kernel and headers
 This package will always depend on the latest 13.10 generic Linux kernel
 and headers, or 14.04 when 13.10 is end of life. Refer to this page for details:
 https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Kernel/LTSEnablementStack

